data.description: Welcome to 3723 Palm Avenue! This charming cape cod sits on a corner lot in the heart of South Lorain. It features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. You will find the first two bedrooms on the main floor. The third bedroom is upstairs and could be used as a spacious master suite which features a large closet as well as its own full bathroom. The living room is spacious, yet cozy which is perfect for those cold Ohio winter nights! The eat-in kitchen is tastefully updated and ready to host your next dinner. The only thing missing is its new owner to enjoy for years to come.
